# Tailwind CSS Styling

- Tailwind v4 via `@tailwindcss/postcss` — there is no `tailwind.config.js`
- Theme is defined in `app/globals.css` using `@theme inline` with CSS custom properties
- Custom variables: `--color-type-*` for Pokémon types, `--color-surface-dark`, `--color-muted`, `--color-foreground`
- Use Tailwind utility classes directly in JSX — no CSS modules, styled-components, or Emotion
- Mobile-first responsive design: use `md:` and `lg:` prefixes for desktop layouts
- For custom non-Tailwind styles, add them to `globals.css` (e.g., `.image-rendering-pixelated`)
